Global Automotive Rear Window Wiper Market Insights
Automotive Rear Window Wiper Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.0% from 2024 to 2030.


Automotive Rear Window Wiper Market Overview
The global automotive rear window wiper market was valued at USD 1.45 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 2.12 billion by 2028, growing at a CAGR of 8.1% during the forecast period. The market is driven by increasing automotive production, advancements in wiper technologies, and growing consumer demand for improved driving safety and visibility in adverse weather conditions. Additionally, the trend towards electric vehicles (EVs) and connected car technologies is further contributing to market expansion.

